WEBVTT

00:12:59.611 --> 00:13:01.974
whatever is in your heart.

00:13:02.847 --> 00:13:05.051
There are websites like DonorsChoose

00:13:05.075 --> 00:13:07.129
that recognize the disparity

00:13:07.153 --> 00:13:09.648
and actually want
to do something about it.

00:13:11.748 --> 00:13:13.952
What is a carpenter with no tools?

00:13:14.350 --> 00:13:16.672
What is an actress with no stage?

00:13:16.990 --> 00:13:19.447
What is a scientist with no laboratory?

00:13:19.859 --> 00:13:22.586
What is a doctor with no equipment?

00:13:23.270 --> 00:13:24.515
I'll tell you:

00:13:24.970 --> 00:13:26.434
they're my kids.

00:13:27.219 --> 00:13:29.035
Shouldn't they be your kids, too?

00:13:29.893 --> 00:13:31.044
Thank you.